Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.56,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}所以迈开步伐启程吧
Comment: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:05.05,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,---ED---
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:12.89,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}昨日よりもきっと　強くなれるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:18.60,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}そんな言葉繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:27.90,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}ちっぽけな　心を試してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:33.45,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}言葉はいらない　顔を上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:41.29,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}夜空を旅しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:46.88,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}僕らが描いた未来は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.47,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}はるか遠い道の途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:23:03.82,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}涙も笑顔も　分かち合えたらいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:09.45,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}遠く光る空の彼方　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.16,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}探したいものがあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:23.42,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}信じよう 一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:29.97,Asteroid - EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:12.89,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}一定会比昨天变得更坚强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:18.60,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}不断地重复着这些话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:27.90,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}考验着小小的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:33.45,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}无需多言  抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:41.29,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}来一次美妙的夜空之旅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:46.88,Asteroid - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}我们所描绘的未来
